      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Law Enforcement Officer Recreation Pass Act</strong></p><p>This bill directs the Forest Service and the Department of the Interior to make the National Parks and Federal Recreational Lands Pass available, without charge and for the lifetime of the passholder, to law enforcement officers.</p>",
